targets.query: SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~ /.*4.7.*unit.*/  AND "state" = 'success' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*4.7.*unit.*/  AND "state" = 'failure' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*4.7.*unit.*/  AND "state" = 'aborted' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "autogen"."build" WHERE ("job_name" =~ /.*unit.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "job_name"
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~ /.*pull.*/  AND "state" = 'success' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*pull.*/  AND "state" = 'failure' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*pull.*/  AND "state" = 'aborted' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~ /.*pull.*4.9.*/  AND "state" = 'success' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*pull.*4.9.*/  AND "state" = 'failure' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*pull.*4.9.*/  AND "state" = 'aborted' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "autogen"."build" WHERE  ("job_name" =~ /.*pull.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "job_name"
